ss=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071820/extras/ba7c966183d6817fce40e4c2460ec766.poster.avif?t=1739711302\" width=512 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071820/extras/ba7c966183d6817fce40e4c2460ec766.webm?t=1739711302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071820/extras/ba7c966183d6817fce40e4c2460ec766.mp4?t=1739711302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Slaughter the undead!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrades, upgrades, upgrades!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071820/extras/e546683acf079165e87292a657cefafd.poster.avif?t=1739711302\" width=600 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071820/extras/e546683acf079165e87292a657cefafd.webm?t=1739711302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071820/extras/e546683acf079165e87292a657cefafd.mp4?t=1739711302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Choose from many unlockable upgrade cards to empower your hero. Choose your own game style, be your own hero!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Deck building with upgrade cards you find along the way<br></li><li> Shop to upgrade your favorite cards<br></li><li> Unique abilities to choose from in your runs<br></li><li> Unique enemies to fight<br></li><li> Skill based gameplay</li></ul><br><strong>Can you break the Lich’s curse and restore peace to the land?</strong>",
